node.text: Can’t believe I’m really having a baby on the way I promised to myself that i will give my baby the life I always wanted as a child & with me having a baby on the way it really makes me think before everything now LOL this so crazy I went from being a kid to now having my own kid I’m excited & ready to be the great father I know I will be..& aw yeah by the way I really don’t care about everybody else opinion because my baby gonna be well taken care of and going to get everything it wants & desire in life I am now welcoming my new generation of me ......🖤
